# Environment
- Windows Powershell
- npm for package manager
- npx expo start for running the development server
- Maintain .env for all API keys, add placeholders if needed

# Architecture
- Firebase for User Authentication
- Firestore for the social media components like posts, comments and messages
- PostgreSQL for transactional data like products, orders
- Backend using FastAPI including separate endpoints to write to the above databases
- For payment, we will use PhonePe Integration, implementation reference - https://www.phonepe.com/guides/payment-gateway/how-to-integrate-payment-gateway-into-your-website-a-complete-guide, https://developer.phonepe.com/v1/docs/api-integration-1/
